flowchart TD
  start([Issue 208 readiness gate]) --> deploy[Inspect latest production deployment]
  deploy --> deployReady{Deployment ready for commit bbf4916?}
  deployReady -->|yes| authConfig[Validate Vercel auth env names]
  deployReady -->|no| blocked[Block pilot and link remediation]

  authConfig --> authSmoke[Run registration auth production smoke]
  authSmoke --> protectedRoutes[Verify /tasks, /projects, and task detail routes]
  protectedRoutes --> authStatus[Run auth status require-complete gate]
  authStatus --> authPass{Auth gate passed?}
  authPass -->|yes| projectsDb[Verify Projects migration 012 and schema columns]
  authPass -->|no| blocked

  projectsDb --> projectsSmoke[Run Projects API smoke]
  projectsSmoke --> projectChecks{CRUD, membership, archive, and tenant isolation passed?}
  projectChecks -->|yes| delegation[Run OpenClaw live delegation smoke]
  projectChecks -->|no| blocked

  delegation --> delegationPass{Runtime-owned agentId and sessionId?}
  delegationPass -->|yes| ready([Pilot ready with fresh evidence])
  delegationPass -->|no| blocked

  blocked --> followup[Create or link remediation issue]
  followup --> rerun[Rerun failed checks after remediation]
  rerun --> authSmoke
